settings.description: REISSUE: Dig up all sorts of surprises in this vertical course. Prod. Code: 103, Rel. Date: 5/16/22. Completely new levels released Wed - 6pm, re-issues Mon 11.15 am
Watch out for the chain chomps.
Try and get the mushroom to the end!
My attempt at making a level.
From boomerang pirouettes to rolling balls of pain .. just jump into the purely psychotic sand -- enemies and all. Made in August of '21 .. updated improvements over the last week.
it 100% does not glitch the game and make it so you cant finish the level. he he he...
The improved version of my other castle: ''Bowser's Revenge'', I hope you like it!
